New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 9pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\">杜导正与资中筠</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; BACKGROUND: white; COLOR: #444444; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal align=center></SPAN></FONT><BR></SPAN></SPAN><BR>　　2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">月</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US>27</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">日上午，“</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US>2013</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">年《炎黄春秋》新春联谊会”在北京大方饭店隆重举行。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">常务社长、总编辑吴思主持联谊会。他向与会嘉宾简单介绍了《炎黄春秋》杂志一年来的发展情况，特别报告大家，《炎黄春秋》杂志发行量逐年攀高，今年比去年同期又增长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US>13%</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">；《炎黄春秋》杂志以各种形式出现在网络上，微博、电子版、</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US>ipad</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">及</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">iPhone</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">版、手机版等得到广大网民的欢迎。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">社长</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">杜导正致辞中对前来参加联谊会的新老朋友表示热烈欢迎和感谢。杜老再次强调，<EM><SPAN style=\"FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">中国的希望在民间，如果真想开创一个新时代，必须实实在在的依靠人民、依靠民间力量。</SPAN></EM></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">李锐、江平、张希清（代表炎黄文化研究会）、资中筠、高尚全、胡德平、李洪林、高锴、钱理群、陆德、胡德华、浦志强、周志兴、钟沛璋、刘苏里、高放、马晓力、蒋彦永等陆续发言，周有光之子代表周老发言。近</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Arial; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" lang=EN-US>200</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">位来宾出席联谊会。<BR>　　本刊第4期将详细介绍此次新春联谊会盛况。<BR></SPAN></P>","title":"“2013年《炎黄春秋》新春联谊会”隆重举行","time":1362427736999}